headline: Qualcomm Increases Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: SAN DIEGO, March 18, 2025--Qualcomm Incorporated (NASDAQ: QCOM) today announced that its Board of Directors has approved an increase in the Company’s quarterly cash dividend from $0.85 to $0.89 per share of common stock. This dividend increase will be effective for quarterly dividends payable after March 27, 2025, and will raise the annualized dividend payout to $3.56 per share of common stock.
